  "ideas": {
    "intro": "Ideas for projects, activities, books, games, and more for students with a high level of interest.",
    "terms": [
      {
        "term": 1,
        "title": "Term 1",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "receoOLZPuYmNwDYl",
            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] [Scouting for Wild Ones](https://agentlefeast.com/product/scoutingbook/) by Brittney McGann is full of great lessons and activities for your budding scout.\n[ ] Choose a museum from [this list](https://studenttravelplanningguide.com/virtual-field-trips/) of museums by state and take a virtual field trip. (A parent should preview all links.)\n[ ] Try a recipe from [one of the states](https://a.co/d/6QqQ4JL) you are studying. Check your library or online for ideas."
          },
          {
            "id": "recdAvmfoOftMiSNw",
            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Enjoy the book [Climbing Kansas Mountains by George Shannon](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RsnkhOwkvSA), read aloud on YouTube."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 2,
        "title": "Term 2",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recjZPlC643sefHkt",
            "term": 2,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Kentucky has more than 130 caves and caverns. Read about seven remarkable ones in this [Smithsonian article](https://www.smithsonianmag.com/sponsored/seven-remarkable-caves-explore-kentucky-180976889/).\n[ ] Visit this amazing[ 3-dimensional map ](https://lh3.ggpht.com/-2FH77Y-374M/UZymFOTGbkI/AAAAAAAAor0/jQSL7DT1hTY/mud-island-riverwalk-2%25255B8%25255D.jpg?imgmax=800)of the lower Mississippi River if you are near Memphis. It is on Mud Island at Riverpark.\n[ ] Learn about the Jr. Ranger Program at this [nps site](https://www.nps.gov/kids/junior-rangers.htm). There are activities you can even do from home."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 3,
        "title": "Term 3",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "recFmRGppvHlis6o4",
            "term": 3,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] Take a [virtual tour](https://www.nationalparks.org/connect/blog/take-virtual-visit-national-park) or watch a webcam from a National Park.\n[ ] Take a [virtual field trip](https://youtu.be/F7K2Vmog8nk?si=asQoMwFrQzttgjxp) to Washington, D.C.\n[ ] You can find out what indigenous groups lived in your zip code by entering it [here](https://land.codeforanchorage.org/)."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
